00:16:58.500 --> 00:16:59.800
"word" with your chest.

00:16:59.800 --> 00:17:01.100
One, two, three.

00:17:01.100 --> 00:17:02.400
&gt;&gt; [multiple speakers] Word!

00:17:02.400 --> 00:17:03.700
&gt;&gt; I appreciate you.

00:17:03.700 --> 00:17:05.000
You can make that sound you make

00:17:05.000 --> 00:17:06.860
