piece of chocolate.

00:17:06.860 --> 00:17:10.430
Mmm. Don't eat chocolate?

00:17:10.430 --> 00:17:11.730
I don't know who you are,

00:17:11.730 --> 00:17:14.690
but if you don't eat
chocolate, think mango.

00:17:14.690 --> 00:17:17.340
Mmm. I feel like
it got less people.

00:17:17.340 --> 00:17:18.640
That's weird.

00:17:18.640 --> 00:17:20.210
I love mango and chocolate,
but I'm just crazy.

00:17:20.210 --> 00:17:21.780
All right.

00:17:21.780 --> 00:17:25.070
Last, but not least, you can
do, what is my favorite way

00:17:25.070 --> 00:17:28.110
of showing appreciation,
you can take the word "she,"

00:17:28.110 --> 00:17:31.020
you can take the word "Jesus,"
and if you hear something

00:17:31.020 --> 00:17:32.320
that makes you feel
particularly holy,

00:17:32.320 --> 00:17:33.620
no matter your religious
denomination,

00:17:33.620 --> 00:17:37.150
you smoosh those words together,
and it becomes "Shesus."

00:17:37.150 --> 00:17:39.290
[ Laughter ]

00:17:39.290 --> 00:17:42.950
Now, what I'm about to do will
be a litmus for how much fun

00:17:42.950 --> 00:17:45.390
and passion and enjoyment
we're gonna get

00:17:45.390 --> 00:17:47.580
out of this event this evening.

00:17:47.580 --> 00:17:49.540
I'm going to ask you,
on the count of three,

00:17:49.540 --> 00:17:51.300
everyone in this room, to
put your right hand up,

00:17:51.300 --> 00:17:53.080
and give me your best Shesus.

00:17:53.080 --> 00:17:55.160
All right?

00:17:55.160 --> 00:17:58.660
From zero to 100%, we're
gonna tell how it's gonna go

00:17:58.660 --> 00:17:59.960
down here.

00:17:59.960 --> 00:18:01.260
All right?

00:18:01.260 --> 00:18:02.560
On the count of three.

00:18:02.560 --> 00:18:03.860
It's better when
you participate!

00:18:03.860 --> 00:18:06.080
I'm bracing myself.

00:18:06.080 --> 00:18:08.910
One, two, three.

00:18:08.910 --> 00:18:10.210
&gt;&gt; [multiple speakers] Shesus!

00:18:10.210 --> 00:18:11.510
&gt;&gt; Ohh!

00:18:11.510 --> 00:18:13.050
[ Laughter ]

00:18:13.050 --> 00:18:15.520
I don't know when you're gonna
have the opportunity to be

00:18:15.520 --> 00:18:17.500
in front of a thousand
people you don't know,

00:18:17.500 --> 00:18:20.650
and have them say the word
"shesus," right hand up to you.

00:18:20.650 --> 00:18:22.280
But if you ever get
that opportunity,

00:18:22.280 --> 00:18:25.040
you should pursue
it relentlessly.

00:18:25.040 --> 00:18:27.070
[ Laughter ]

00:18:27.070 --> 00:18:29.790
Are you ready for a poetry slam?

00:18:29.790 --> 00:18:31.090
Say "word."

00:18:31.090 --> 00:18:32.390
&gt;&gt; [multiple speakers] Word!

00:18:32.390 --> 00:18:33.690
&gt;&gt; You are not ready
