00:18:33.690 --> 00:18:34.990
&gt;&gt; Why not?

00:18:34.990 --> 00:18:36.290
&gt;&gt; And I'll tell you why not,

00:18:36.290 --> 00:18:38.220
because before we have a poetry
slam, we must have a poet come

00:18:38.220 --> 00:18:43.000
to the stage and calibrate our
judges, because they're rusty.

00:18:43.000 --> 00:18:44.900
It's been a year since
we've been here, right?

00:18:44.900 --> 00:18:46.530
We gotta make sure that
they're ready for this,

00:18:46.530 --> 00:18:48.100
because this is real serious.

