So we bring what we
call a sacrificial poet

00:18:50.110 --> 00:18:51.410
up to the stage --

00:18:51.410 --> 00:18:53.410
[ Cheering ]

00:18:53.410 --> 00:18:54.710
And she performs.

00:18:54.710 --> 00:18:56.010
Oh, I gave it away.

