01:11:46.290 --> 01:11:47.590
&gt;&gt; [speaking in a
child's voice] Hi,

01:11:47.590 --> 01:11:49.850
my name Michele [assumed
spelling] and I four year old.

01:11:49.850 --> 01:11:51.760
Mommy and Daddy not
together no more,

01:11:51.760 --> 01:11:53.530
but there's still
my third Christmas.

01:11:53.530 --> 01:11:56.310
This year I spent
at Daddy house.

01:11:56.310 --> 01:11:59.180
Momma bought me Apple Bottom
jeans, and daddy bought me boots

01:11:59.180 --> 01:12:02.250
with the fur, so you
know how I rockin' it.

01:12:02.250 --> 01:12:04.410
My stepbrother say he got
a special present for me.

01:12:04.410 --> 01:12:07.230
And I just can't wait to see it.

01:12:07.230 --> 01:12:09.780
I really hate surprises,
so I keep bugging.

01:12:09.780 --> 01:12:12.110
He told me don't worry
because it's real big.

01:12:12.110 --> 01:12:14.360
My stepbrother's
really the best.

01:12:14.360 --> 01:12:17.060
He took me to the back room,
he gave me the biggest piece

01:12:17.060 --> 01:12:21.230
of candy -- or I thought
it was a piece of candy.

01:12:21.230 --> 01:12:23.980
I was scared, but who backs

01:12:23.980 --> 01:12:25.370
down to sweets [end
speaking in a child's voice]?

01:12:25.370 --> 01:12:30.050
It's always just
been me and my mom.

01:12:30.050 --> 01:12:32.270
I couldn't believe it when
she said I couldn't go

01:12:32.270 --> 01:12:33.570
to my dad's anymore.

01:12:33.570 --> 01:12:35.460
Every time I came
back from his house

01:12:35.460 --> 01:12:37.090
in the summer I gained
a little weight.

01:12:37.090 --> 01:12:39.920
I didn't know if it was
because of the depression,

01:12:39.920 --> 01:12:42.750
or all the candy.

01:12:42.750 --> 01:12:45.210
My father said she was just
trying to keep me away from him.

01:12:45.210 --> 01:12:48.450
But I guess he never noticed
my stepbrother's sweet tooth.

01:12:48.450 --> 01:12:51.070
I hated my mom.

01:12:51.070 --> 01:12:52.610
When in reality,
she was just trying

01:12:52.610 --> 01:12:55.250
to protect me from other sweets.

01:12:55.250 --> 01:12:57.620
But by the time the
cavities came in,

01:12:57.620 --> 01:12:59.740
there wasn't really
much she could do,

01:12:59.740 --> 01:13:02.030
because Medi-Cal
wouldn't cover it.

01:13:02.030 --> 01:13:05.010
The therapist wouldn't
take our insurance.

01:13:05.010 --> 01:13:07.360
Nobody to help.

01:13:07.360 --> 01:13:11.200
My tooth began to decay, and
it felt like I was rotting

01:13:11.200 --> 01:13:14.560
from inside to out,
turning white

01:13:14.560 --> 01:13:17.790
to yellow to brown to black.

01:13:17.790 --> 01:13:20.880
And I'm still rotting.

01:13:20.880 --> 01:13:23.600
I always knew diabetes
were genetic,

01:13:23.600 --> 01:13:26.660
but I never knew you could catch
a disease from a sweet tooth.

01:13:26.660 --> 01:13:31.850
I'm the cutest 16-year-old
you'll ever see.

01:13:31.850 --> 01:13:35.120
These dudes stay hitting
me, but I don't want them,

01:13:35.120 --> 01:13:36.420
because all they
wanna do is hit.

01:13:36.420 --> 01:13:39.440
I met this one dude, and I
think I kind of like him.

01:13:39.440 --> 01:13:42.880
But every time he hugs me
and his hands touch my waist,

01:13:42.880 --> 01:13:44.440
I begin to feel wasted.

01:13:44.440 --> 01:13:48.690
Like, uh, uh, like I
forgot how to talk.

01:13:48.690 --> 01:13:52.020
Anyways, I'm hecka grown, and I
don't need a dude for nothing.

01:13:52.020 --> 01:14:00.280
I got all these girls hecka mad
because their dude wants me.

01:14:00.280 --> 01:14:05.140
But my father just got out of
jail, and he swear he father

01:14:05.140 --> 01:14:10.160
of the year, but where was
here when I got cavities?

01:14:10.160 --> 01:14:18.650
Where was he to help pay
to repair my sweet tooth?

01:14:18.650 --> 01:14:22.580
He tried to come in
my life and raise me

01:14:22.580 --> 01:14:26.150
like I wasn't already grown.

01:14:26.150 --> 01:14:28.410
I got enough dudes.

01:14:28.410 --> 01:14:29.710
I don't need him.

01:14:29.710 --> 01:14:31.560
I be straight hustlin'.

01:14:31.560 --> 01:14:40.290
I got a dude who get my nails
done, one to pay my phone bill,

01:14:40.290 --> 01:14:44.610
one to take me out, and,
of course, one for pipe.

01:14:44.610 --> 01:14:50.140
Oh, and I work at
the CVS Center.

01:14:50.140 --> 01:14:54.610
These customers hella annoying.

01:14:54.610 --> 01:14:56.580
Hello. Welcome to
the CVS Center.

01:14:56.580 --> 01:14:57.880
How may I help you?

01:14:57.880 --> 01:14:59.490
I never thought I'd
feel like this again.

01:14:59.490 --> 01:15:01.980
It's so hot in here.

01:15:01.980 --> 01:15:03.280
I'm starting to get anxiety.

01:15:03.280 --> 01:15:05.510
I -- I -- I can't breathe.

01:15:05.510 --> 01:15:06.810
Can they turn the air on?

01:15:06.810 --> 01:15:09.290
It's like -- it's like the devil
himself is standing in front

01:15:09.290 --> 01:15:10.600
of me pulling me down to hell.

01:15:10.600 --> 01:15:11.900
I went on my break.

01:15:11.900 --> 01:15:13.200
I called my momma.

01:15:13.200 --> 01:15:15.000
I told her I saw my stepbrother,
and he smiled at me.

01:15:15.000 --> 01:15:31.040
[ Cheering and Applause ]

01:15:31.040 --> 01:15:34.910
&gt;&gt; So every year Split This
