01:15:34.910 --> 01:15:39.440
It's an opportunity where
they open up the contest

01:15:39.440 --> 01:15:41.250
to all members of the community.

01:15:41.250 --> 01:15:45.540
It is called the Sonia
Sanchez-Langston Hughes

01:15:45.540 --> 01:15:46.840
Poetry Contest.

01:15:46.840 --> 01:15:50.250
Let's put a little
weight behind it, right?

01:15:50.250 --> 01:15:51.960
We're not playing around.

01:15:51.960 --> 01:15:53.910
There's some good examples
that we're looking to.

