01:16:01.260 --> 01:16:05.590
So if you don't know
who Franny Choi is,

01:16:05.590 --> 01:16:07.920
and you just heard these young
people get really excited

01:16:07.920 --> 01:16:14.250
about it, do two things: one,
look up Franny Choi; and, two,

01:16:14.250 --> 01:16:19.410
go to splitthisrock.org
and contribute your poetry

01:16:19.410 --> 01:16:21.210
to this poetry contest.

01:16:21.210 --> 01:16:24.780
First place winner, 500 bucks
