over, when we're left

01:20:29.510 --> 01:20:31.190
in the corner of
everyone's eyes.

01:20:31.190 --> 01:20:34.510
Our dance outcast into
spotlight, hitting VOC

01:20:34.510 --> 01:20:36.750
